<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Digital Business Card</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
}

body{

background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6d5dfc,#46c2ff);
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
height:100vh;

}

.card{

width:340px;
background:white;
border-radius:20px;
overflow:hidden;
box-shadow:0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
transition:.4s;

}

.card:hover{

transform:translateY(-8px);

}

.cover{

height:120px;
background:linear-gradient(90deg,#4f46e5,#06b6d4);

}

.profile{

display:flex;
justify-content:center;
margin-top:-45px;

}

.profile img{

width:90px;
height:90px;
border-radius:50%;
border:5px solid white;
object-fit:cover;

}

.content{

padding:20px;
text-align:center;

}

h2{

color:#333;

}

.role{

color:#4f46e5;
margin:8px 0 15px;

}

.bio{

font-size:14px;
color:#666;
line-height:22px;

}

.stats{

display:flex;
justify-content:space-around;
margin:20px 0;

}

.box h3{

color:#4f46e5;

}

.box p{

font-size:13px;
color:#777;

}

.buttons{

display:flex;
justify-content:center;
gap:10px;

}

button{

padding:10px 18px;
border:none;
border-radius:8px;
cursor:pointer;
font-size:14px;

}

.follow{

background:#4f46e5;
color:white;

}

.message{

background:#eef2ff;
color:#4f46e5;

}

.footer{

padding:15px;
text-align:center;
font-size:13px;
color:gray;

}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="card">

<div class="cover"></div>

<div class="profile">

<img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=12">

</div>

<div class="content">

<h2>Nikitha K</h2>

<p class="role">
Frontend Developer
</p>

<p class="bio">
Passionate about AI, Web Development and creating real-world solutions through modern technology.
</p>

<div class="stats">

<div class="box">
<h3>12</h3>
<p>Projects</p>
</div>

<div class="box">
<h3>5</h3>
<p>Hackathons</p>
</div>

<div class="box">
<h3>8</h3>
<p>Certificates</p>
</div>

</div>

<div class="buttons">

<button class="follow">
Follow
</button>

<button class="message">
Message
</button>

</div>

</div>

<div class="footer">

Designed with HTML & CSS ❤️

</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
